version: 1.0.3
version_description: Move drunk stages and vehicle interactions into Config.Drunk and add Config.UseRCoreDrunk flag; update Drunk logic to read settings from config, throttle vehicle interactions, and use SetTimeout for pause handling. Add rcore_drunk integration gate and warn if enabled but missing. Implement manual item animation/prop spawning while progress bar runs (attach/delete props and clear tasks after), and disable progressBar's built-in anim/prop fields. Rename debug flag usage to Config.Debug. Add a new animation entry (mp_suicide::pill) and bump fxmanifest version to 1.0.3. Minor misc. fixes and cleanup across client files.